      "text": "总会过分要命的囧",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 104.15,
      "time_str": "01:44.150",
      "text": "在过去每个时候我都会想象的念头",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 110.94,
      "time_str": "01:50.940",
      "text": "别怕就算我是你的",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 113.09,
